{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9d2011d9ed","title":"关于军队支左的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bd94d45bb6","index":0,"year":1967,"month":7,"day":15,"articleId":"9d2011d9ed","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"军队和军事","id":"6f7a683373","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9d6b30bf5e","type":"title","text":"关于军队支左的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9d2011d9ed","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0f0f3ca31f","type":"paragraph","text":"支左有很大好处，就是使军队本身受到教育，他们会从实际斗争中体会到这个问题。支左不仅支革命群众，支左派组织，不但看到社会各方面存在两条路线的斗争，同时也能看到军队里存在两条路线的斗争。要看到阶级斗争也反映到军队里边，军队通过支左，把问题暴露在社会上，从而更加提高我们军队的思想水平，这才是辩证唯物主义。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"9d2011d9ed","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}